{"tid":1761654,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴奧脫福贏波會否剷草？","createTime":"2019-11-29T05:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T05:23:05.000Z","uid":213952,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff9c724044e8238c29ed359bf1b721468d18d6f","tid":1761654,"uid":213952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc63b726180284b4937fe585709be9cfb5df364","tid":1761654,"uid":213952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ff9c724044e8238c29ed359bf1b721468d18d6f","tid":1761654,"uid":213952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"曼狗"},{"pid":"f7cf8c1007c7e7f1052c1357a5e48e8bd36a2901","tid":1761654,"uid":198590,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:02:44.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#213952 - 高達賓撕馬</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span>, 請大家多加注意, 善用不推文回覆！<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>潘曉穎既父母呢一刻有咩感覺？ - #53</code><br />\n<blockquote>搵泛民一早私了左，唔洗煩</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1673789/page/3?ref=sharer&amp;post=53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1673789/page/3?ref=sharer&amp;post=53</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>[即時討論] 遮打花園開始多人 - #2183</code><br />\n<blockquote>無腦前線：我知道你地未必有機會接受教育，又唔會喺中環返工，可能集會用英文你未必聽得明，但請尊重中環人一次，尊重和理非決定！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fcry.gif&h=dd1dbdee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1653788/page/88?ref=sharer&amp;post=2183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1653788/page/88?ref=sharer&amp;post=2183</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>[即時討論] 遮打花園開始多人 - #2158</code><br />\n<blockquote>前線請考慮到自己智力低，唔好亂行動，唔好迫中環人接受你既無腦決定！</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1653788/page/87?ref=sharer&amp;post=2158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1653788/page/87?ref=sharer&amp;post=2158</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>前線已失控，向記者擲燃燒彈 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>【港島即時】1755 杜老誌道大公報對出，Now新聞台記者及攝影師被燃燒彈擊中，二人的頭盔及攝影機起火。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/photos/pcb.3253955451298313/3253953914631800/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusu.cbc%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.3253955451298313%2F3253953914631800%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=23339df0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/photos/pcb.3253955451298313/3253953914631800/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一、重組前線，要求有一定學歷智力先得<br />\n二、停止無差別攻擊，對準政權<br />\n三、不再高舉「前線決定」<br />\n四、和理非不是condom，無必要次次幫低智前線執屎<br />\n</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1629758/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1629758/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>又話無大台？記者會代表誰？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fsmile.gif&h=d434394b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fsmile.gif&h=d434394b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fsmile.gif&h=d434394b&s={SIZE}\" />人唔笑</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1419943/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1419943/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"b57769e428cb352fd4afd018635db8dc24296bc6","tid":1761654,"uid":61660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:03:48.000Z","msg":"不如試下奧脫福再現呢幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/1ndLCzrbROHba/giphy.gif?cid=790b7611a293cd259c8a751fc411c66ff4669ed2e606cf44&amp;rid=giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia0.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1ndLCzrbROHba%2Fgiphy.gif%3Fcid%3D790b7611a293cd259c8a751fc411c66ff4669ed2e606cf44%26rid%3Dgiphy.gif&h=7bbee917&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e666116118484833e3c5dfcc5cbd315c29396eac","tid":1761654,"uid":213952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b57769e428cb352fd4afd018635db8dc24296bc6","tid":1761654,"uid":61660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:03:48.000Z","msg":"不如試下奧脫福再現呢幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/1ndLCzrbROHba/giphy.gif?cid=790b7611a293cd259c8a751fc411c66ff4669ed2e606cf44&amp;rid=giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia0.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1ndLCzrbROHba%2Fgiphy.gif%3Fcid%3D790b7611a293cd259c8a751fc411c66ff4669ed2e606cf44%26rid%3Dgiphy.gif&h=7bbee917&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"可以考慮"},{"pid":"9d9167f65ac201ac9d1fa298c714ad75345ef4f5","tid":1761654,"uid":213952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"sob好似好憎摩佬，成日串佢"},{"pid":"27a9f3ebceed9605e200e1ebcc5e4c079f1f18c